<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2018-11-17</DATELINE><TITLE>Ocular Examination and Corneal Surface Disease in the Ferret</TITLE><BODY>This article provides a brief, clinically relevant review of corneal surface disease in the ferret. A description of the ophthalmic examination of the ferret is provided. Stepwise descriptions of the most common ophthalmic abnormalities are provided, along with common rule-outs.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>